<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('../partials/head') %>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>
    <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

    <main class="container" style="padding: 40px 20px; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <div class="intro-header" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px; background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541888946425-d81bb19240f5?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80'); background-size: cover; background-position: center; padding: 100px 20px; border-radius: 12px; color: white;">
            <h1 style="color: white; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 700; text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);">Smart Municipal Water Supply Monitoring</h1>
            <p style="font-size: 1.4rem; color: #f0f0f0; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.6; text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);">
                A digital platform designed to bridge the communication gap between the municipal corporation and citizens, ensuring transparency and reliability in water services.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Features Grid -->
        <div class="feature-grid" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 40px; margin-bottom: 80px;">
            <!-- Feature 1 -->
            <div class="feature-card" style="background: white; padding: 40px 30px; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); text-align: center; border-top: 5px solid var(--secondary-blue);">
                <div style="width: 80px; height: 80px; background: var(--light-blue); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 25px;">
                    <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt" style="font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--primary-blue);"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 style="color: var(--dark-blue); margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 1.4rem;">Area-wise Schedules</h3>
                <p style="color: #666;">View centralized, exact water supply timings for your specific area. Plan your day with confidence knowing exactly when water will be available.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 2 -->
            <div class="feature-card" style="background: white; padding: 40px 30px; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); text-align: center; border-top: 5px solid #e63946;">
                <div style="width: 80px; height: 80px; background: #ffe5e7; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 25px;">
                    <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle" style="font-size: 2.5rem; color: #e63946;"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 style="color: var(--dark-blue); margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 1.4rem;">Real-time Notices</h3>
                <p style="color: #666;">Stay informed with instant alerts about water cuts, maintenance work, and service interruptions in your locality.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Feature 3 -->
            <div class="feature-card" style="background: white; padding: 40px 30px; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); text-align: center; border-top: 5px solid var(--primary-blue);">
                <div style="width: 80px; height: 80px; background: var(--light-blue); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 25px;">
                    <i class="fas fa-tint" style="font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--primary-blue);"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 style="color: var(--dark-blue); margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 1.4rem;">Live Quality Status</h3>
                <p style="color: #666;">Access real-time data on water quality to ensure the health and safety of your family. Transparency is our priority.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Info Section -->
        <div class="info-section" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--white) 0%, var(--light-blue) 100%); padding: 50px; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 50px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 300px;">
                <h2 style="color: var(--dark-blue); margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 2rem;">Empowering Citizens</h2>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #444;">
                    In many cities, water is supplied at different times in different areas, but there is no centralized system to inform citizens. This lack of information disrupts daily life.
                </p>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #444;">
                    <strong>Our solution changes that.</strong> By providing a single source of truth for all water-related information, we help you plan better and stay safe.
                </p>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 15px; margin-top: 30px;">
                    <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 50px; color: var(--primary-blue); font-weight: 600;">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Conservation
                    </div>
                    <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 50px; color: var(--primary-blue); font-weight: 600;">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Public Health
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 300px;">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581093458791-9f3c3900df4b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Smart Water Management" style="width: 100%; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); object-fit: cover; height: 350px;">
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>